{"root":{"data":{"id":"d6a9h152s1k0","created":1734061424820,"text":"总"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa4tbfsx40","created":1734063288530,"text":"坚定信仰信念信心","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa5sjra340","created":1734063365221,"text":"增强对马克思主义，共产主义的信仰"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa65zlb480","created":1734063394476,"text":"为什么要信仰马克思主义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa6h9i4dk0","created":1734063419020,"text":"马克思主义是我们认识世界，改变世界的强大思想武器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa6j1c9600","created":1734063422880,"text":"马克思主义是科学的理论，创造性的揭示了人类社会发展规律"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa6trk4uo0","created":1734063446233,"text":"马克思主义是人民的理论，第一次创立了人民实现自身解放的思想体系"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa6wkprmo0","created":1734063452350,"text":"马克思主义是实践的理论，指引者 人民该改造世界的行动"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa70squ8g0","created":1734063461542,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa68zfwww0","created":1734063400997,"text":"胸怀共产主义远大理想"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa5vxfdzc0","created":1734063372577,"text":"增强对中国特色社会主义的信念"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa5yxkxyg0","created":1734063379117,"text":"增强对实现中华民族伟大复兴的信心"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa4voie400","created":1734063293674,"text":"理想信念的内涵及重要性","layout_mind_offset":{"x":30.99999953806403,"y":62.9999990612269},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9snx4tk80","created":1734062336411,"text":"什么是理想信念","expandState":"expand","priority":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9i4wsf6g0","created":1734061511390,"text":"信念"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9ojq9bcw0","created":1734062013832,"text":"内涵"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9okm8ut40","created":1734062015766,"text":"人们在一定的认识基础上，对某种思想或事物坚信不疑并身体力行的态度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9r6n8lls0","created":1734062220443,"text":"认知，情感和意志的有机统一体"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9ot6otu00","created":1734062034416,"text":"特征"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9ox0mu7c0","created":1734062042757,"text":"执着性：一旦形成，不易改变。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9oxtwzio0","created":1734062044528,"text":"支撑性：信念凝聚着一个国家，一个民族的集体意志，为社会理想的实现提供强\n 大的精神力量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9oyg429s0","created":1734062045870,"text":"多样性：不同人由于社会环境，思想观念，利益需要，人生经历和性格特征等方\n 面的差异，会形成不同的信念"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9i9uqm9c0","created":1734061522150,"text":"理想","layout_right_offset":{"x":29.999999552965164,"y":3.9999999403953552}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9iu1yuqo0","created":1734061566123,"text":"内涵","layout_right_offset":{"x":21.999999672174567,"y":7.999999880790654}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9j3hjqqw0","created":1734061586656,"text":"理想是人们在实践中形成的、有实现可能性的、对未来社会和自身发展的向往和追求。","layout_right_offset":{"x":17.00000424683094,"y":-12.999999806284904}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9rzrjgn40","created":1734062283830,"text":"人们的世界观，人生观和价值观在奋斗目标上的集中体现","layout_right_offset":{"x":24.99999962747097,"y":4.999999925494194}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9j072pog0","created":1734061579492,"text":"特征","layout_right_offset":{"x":17.999999731778985,"y":37.99999943375576}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9jiy3fog0","created":1734061620308,"text":"超越性：来源现实，超越现实，指向未来。","layout_right_offset":{"x":37.99999943375576,"y":-14.99999977648261},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9jjdelso0","created":1734061621234,"text":" 实践性：在特定历史条件下的人们对社会实践活动理性认识的结晶，在实践中形成，通过实践来实现。","layout_right_offset":{"x":57.00000603497017,"y":-14.999999776482554}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9jjtznfk0","created":1734061622237,"text":"时代性：受时代条件的制约，随着时代发展而发展","layout_right_offset":{"x":50.999999240040665,"y":-12.999999806284961}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9vqjrzvk0","created":1734062577227,"text":"紧密联系","layout_right_offset":{"x":55.99999916553497,"y":50.999999240040665}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9vvnfkkg0","created":1734062588331,"text":"理想是信念所指的对象。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9wjsi7uo0","created":1734062640881,"text":"信念是理想实现的保障。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9tgkrcyw0","created":1734062398790,"text":"理想信念是精神之“钙”","progress":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9u9m38io0","created":1734062461997,"text":"理想信念的意义","layout_right_offset":{"x":400.99999402463436,"y":51.999999225139504}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9yc9jmhs0","created":1734062781225,"text":"理想指引方向，信念决定成败。","layout_right_offset":{"x":478.99999286234413,"y":160.999997600913}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9yqm9izk0","created":1734062812469,"text":"理想信念昭示奋斗目标","layout_right_offset":{"x":383.9999942779541,"y":168.99999748170382}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9z7ve0q00","created":1734062850026,"text":"理想信念一旦确立就可以使人方向明确，精神振奋，永不迷失前进方向。","layout_right_offset":{"x":726.9999983459711,"y":-46.99999929964554}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9zk4o02o0","created":1734062876709,"text":"人的理想信念反映的是对社会和人的自身发展的期望","layout_right_offset":{"x":662.9999901205302,"y":30.999999538064003}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9zw0yfq00","created":1734062902606,"text":"理想信念催生前进动力","layout_right_offset":{"x":397.9999940693382,"y":206.99999691545975}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa00u7fbk0","created":1734062913082,"text":"一个人有了崇高坚定的理想信念，才会以惊人的毅力和不懈的努力成就事业","layout_right_offset":{"x":704.9999894946815,"y":-28.99999956786644}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa0409vq00","created":1734062919979,"text":"如果没有崇高的理想信念，就有可能浑浑噩噩，庸庸碌碌，虚度一生","layout_right_offset":{"x":682.999989822507,"y":36.999999448657036}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa0bi4o9c0","created":1734062936296,"text":"理想信念提供精神支柱","layout_right_offset":{"x":414.99999381601845,"y":319.99999523162836}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa0fvxqyo0","created":1734062945838,"text":"理想信念是一个人在精神生活领域的“安身立命”的根本","layout_right_offset":{"x":614.999990835786,"y":-44.999999329447746}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa0mc8txs0","created":1734062959885,"text":"理想信念能使人们在遭遇挫折，经受考验的时候，做到知难而进，迎难而上，顽\n强奋斗直至战胜艰难险阻。","layout_right_offset":{"x":730.9999891072507,"y":0.9999999850989525}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa0w6m30g0","created":1734062981312,"text":"理想信念提高精神境界","layout_right_offset":{"x":412.99999384582065,"y":392.99999414384376},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa125slaw0","created":1734062994323,"text":"使人的精神生活各方面统一起来，使人的精神世界成为一个健康有序的系统，避免精神空虚和迷茫。","layout_right_offset":{"x":807.9999879598619,"y":5.9999999105931465}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa1bp5mjs0","created":1734063015085,"text":"引导人们不断追求更高的人生目标，在追求和实现理想的过程中提升理想境界，\n塑造高尚人格。","layout_right_offset":{"x":699.9999895691874,"y":15.999999761581421}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9utfpxuo0","created":1734062505147,"text":"理想信念与大学生","layout_right_offset":{"x":430.9999935775995,"y":519.9999922513962}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6aa23x3wv40","created":1734063076516,"text":"树立崇高的理想信念","layout_right_offset":{"x":351.9999947547914,"y":-32.99999950826168}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa2oq17bs0","created":1734063121800,"text":"将个人的奋斗志向同国家和民族的前途命运紧紧联系在一起。","layout_right_offset":{"x":569.9999915063382,"y":-15.999999761581421}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6aa3q0702w0","created":1734063202956,"text":"把个人的学习进步同祖国的繁荣昌盛紧紧联系起来。","layout_right_offset":{"x":528.9999921172858,"y":2.9999999552965164}},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}